WEBVTT

00:08.207 --> 00:10.308
Finn:
I'm leaving the island.

00:10.310 --> 00:12.811
I'm leaving my mom.

00:12.813 --> 00:15.647
What a wild adventure,
yellow stretching dog.

00:15.649 --> 00:17.683
You said it,
beautiful baby boy.

00:17.685 --> 00:19.217
[ Rumbling ]
Huh?     Huh?

00:22.522 --> 00:23.789
The guardian!

00:23.791 --> 00:24.890
Oh, no!

00:24.892 --> 00:26.958
We never should've left
the island!

00:26.960 --> 00:29.027
Now we die!

00:32.799 --> 00:35.233
Minerva: <i>See? You die.</i>

00:35.235 --> 00:39.971
<i>By my calculations,</i>
<i>you stand a 0.00001% chance</i>

00:39.973 --> 00:41.673
<i>of making it</i>
<i>past the guardian.</i>

00:41.675 --> 00:43.008
Can't you just
turn him off?

00:43.010 --> 00:45.077
<i>He's here</i>
<i>for our protection.</i>

00:45.079 --> 00:47.079
<i>If we were tough enough</i>
<i>to make it past him,</i>

00:47.081 --> 00:48.814
<i>we wouldn't need him!</i>

00:48.816 --> 00:49.848
But...

00:49.850 --> 00:51.383
<i>But none of that matters,</i>

00:51.385 --> 00:53.518
<i>because you can stay safe</i>
<i>right here with me!</i>

00:53.520 --> 00:56.488
<i>Minerva bot,</i>
<i>hug my son again.</i>

00:56.490 --> 00:59.658
Mom, listen, I'm so happy
I finally got to meet you

00:59.660 --> 01:01.026
and learn about humans.

01:01.028 --> 01:03.495
But I have to get back
to my life eventually.

01:03.497 --> 01:06.098
<i>Did you see the simulation?</i>
<i>You'd die!</i>

01:06.100 --> 01:07.599
<i>Let's watch it again.</i>

01:07.601 --> 01:09.401
[ Tape rewinding ]

01:11.038 --> 01:13.004
[ Indistinct conversations,
laughter ]

01:13.006 --> 01:14.773
[ Bells jingle ]

01:14.775 --> 01:16.108
Be right with you.

01:16.110 --> 01:18.276
Excuse me.
Where's the soup?

01:18.278 --> 01:19.411
Ugh.

01:19.413 --> 01:21.747
I told you yesterday --
We are a toy store.

01:21.749 --> 01:24.082
We don't sell sou--
Wooh?

01:25.585 --> 01:27.185
Hi, Frieda.

01:27.187 --> 01:29.855
Kara.
What are <i>you</i> doing here?

01:29.857 --> 01:32.858
Hope you didn't come
to get the soup!

01:33.626 --> 01:37.395
I, um, I wanted to apologize
for everything.

01:37.397 --> 01:39.965
You knew there was more to life
than just the islands,

01:39.967 --> 01:42.134
and I --
I didn't bElieve you.

01:42.136 --> 01:44.736
I know you can't
ever forgive me,

01:44.738 --> 01:47.072
but I <i>am</i> truly sorry.

01:47.074 --> 01:49.074
Don't sweat it.

01:49.076 --> 01:51.042
Awkward feelings averted.

01:51.044 --> 01:52.577
Let's have some soup!

01:52.579 --> 01:55.580
And who's this little
electronic cutie?

01:55.582 --> 01:57.149
What happened to you?

01:57.151 --> 02:01.720
I grew up, and I learned
to accept the Founders' truth.

02:01.722 --> 02:03.989
Frieda.

02:05.124 --> 02:07.125
The outside world's
really cool.

02:07.127 --> 02:08.493
I have cool friends.

02:08.495 --> 02:09.427
Yeah!

02:09.429 --> 02:11.163
I live
in a cool tree house.

02:11.165 --> 02:11.997
Yeah!

02:11.999 --> 02:13.765
I go on cool quests.
Yeah!

02:13.767 --> 02:15.267
<i>That sounds dangerous!</i>

02:15.269 --> 02:16.334
No!

02:16.336 --> 02:19.104
But people need danger
in order to grow.

02:19.106 --> 02:21.339
How will y'all survive
when you leave the island?

02:21.341 --> 02:23.608
<i>Leaving the island</i>
<i>would destroy us.</i>

02:23.610 --> 02:26.111
<i>Besides,</i>
<i>why would they want to leave?</i>

02:26.113 --> 02:27.946
<i>We have everything</i>
<i>you could need.</i>

02:27.948 --> 02:29.014
<i>You hungry?</i>

02:29.016 --> 02:30.515
[ Snaps fingers ]
Always.

02:30.517 --> 02:33.518
<i>Minerva bot, please show him</i>
<i>today's specials.</i>

02:37.156 --> 02:39.424
Minerva bot: Happy home burgers
with choco fries

02:39.426 --> 02:42.027
and our famous
cozy banana split blankie.

02:42.029 --> 02:45.030
Gimme all them specials
in one bowl.

02:47.533 --> 02:49.634
[ Munching loudly ]

02:49.636 --> 02:50.635
Jake!

02:50.637 --> 02:52.103
<i>I'm so glad you like it.</i>

02:52.105 --> 02:53.338
[ Munching continues ]

02:53.340 --> 02:55.207
If you're not gonna hear
what I'm saying,

02:55.209 --> 02:56.641
then look
inside my head!

02:56.643 --> 02:57.943
Danger zone!

02:57.945 --> 02:59.344
[ Zap ]

03:10.990 --> 03:12.057
<i>Finn!</i>

03:12.059 --> 03:14.125
I'm okay.

03:14.127 --> 03:16.027
Sweet remembrances, bro.

03:16.029 --> 03:17.996
<i>Your world seems</i>
<i>so chaotic.</i>

03:17.998 --> 03:21.166
<i>Your ruler's a piece of gum,</i>
<i>your friend's a vampire,</i>

03:21.168 --> 03:22.467
<i>you dated a bit of fire.</i>

03:22.469 --> 03:25.003
<i>Your life</i>
<i>is constantly in danger!</i>

03:25.005 --> 03:27.305
It's my home.
It's where I belong.

03:27.307 --> 03:30.475
<i>As your mother, I think</i>
<i>you belong somewhere safe.</i>

03:30.477 --> 03:33.511
<i>It's not your responsibility</i>
<i>to fight monsters all the time.</i>

03:33.513 --> 03:37.349
<i>Let the grass kid do it --</i>
<i>or the vampire girl.</i>

03:37.351 --> 03:41.219
<i>Minerva bot 5,</i>
<i>ready the cloud chamber.</i>

03:42.855 --> 03:45.223
<i>Now, be a good boy</i>
<i>and get into this machine</i>

03:45.225 --> 03:47.525
<i>so it can juice up</i>
<i>your precious essence.</i>

03:47.527 --> 03:48.660
[ Gasps ]

03:48.662 --> 03:50.528
Pftttt!

03:50.530 --> 03:51.529
[ Munching ]

03:51.531 --> 03:52.998
[ Sighs ]

03:53.000 --> 03:55.233
Mom, not only
am I not getting juiced,

03:55.235 --> 03:58.336
I'm gonna leave this place
and take everyone to freedom!

03:58.338 --> 04:00.739
<i>Okay, sweetie,</i>
<i>but I think you'll find</i>

04:00.741 --> 04:02.540
<i>everyone's pretty happy here.</i>

04:02.542 --> 04:06.378
It's true.
I'm really, really happy here.

04:06.380 --> 04:09.447
Don't you remember
your dreams of exploration?

04:10.249 --> 04:14.686
If I remember,
I might get...angry.

04:14.688 --> 04:19.057
You    <i>shou</i>be angry --
at <i>me.</i>

04:19.059 --> 04:21.693
Nah. I'm over it.

04:21.695 --> 04:24.229
[ Indistinct conversations ]
Finn: Hey, everyone!

04:24.231 --> 04:27.065
Uh, excuse me.

04:27.067 --> 04:28.233
[ High-pitched scream ]

04:28.235 --> 04:29.567
[ Conversations stop ]

04:29.569 --> 04:31.937
I know y'all like
living on this tiny island

04:31.939 --> 04:33.271
'cause it's safe and chill,

04:33.273 --> 04:35.507
but you don't have to live
like this.

04:36.275 --> 04:38.410
[ Crowd murmuring ]

04:38.412 --> 04:39.444
Wait!

04:39.446 --> 04:41.246
You think
the outside world is scary?

04:41.248 --> 04:43.315
Well, you know
what's <i>really</i> scary?

04:43.317 --> 04:43.982
Bees!

04:43.984 --> 04:44.883
Germs!

04:44.885 --> 04:45.750
Frogs!

04:45.752 --> 04:46.818
Crowds!

04:46.820 --> 04:47.819
Ngyuhhh!

04:47.821 --> 04:49.220
No.

04:49.222 --> 04:51.623
Letting fear make
all your decisions for you.

04:51.625 --> 04:53.625
[ Crowd murmuring ]

04:53.627 --> 04:57.062
You! Do you know
you have free will?

04:57.064 --> 04:59.331
Is -- Is that
what you're selling?

05:00.232 --> 05:03.168
You got to --
How do you even -- Ugh!

05:03.170 --> 05:05.103
Finn: How do you even know
if you're happy

05:05.105 --> 05:07.005
if someone else decided
for you?

05:07.007 --> 05:08.440
Follow me!

05:08.442 --> 05:10.775
Don't you want to be able
to choose what you do?

05:10.777 --> 05:12.077
And where you go?

05:12.079 --> 05:13.912
Crowd: Sounds hard.

05:13.914 --> 05:15.914
Yeah, but it's also fun.

05:15.916 --> 05:17.849
And boring.
And good and bad.

05:17.851 --> 05:19.117
Life's never just one thing.

05:19.119 --> 05:20.485
Yeah.

05:20.487 --> 05:22.754
We got freedom
smushed up inside our guts.

05:22.756 --> 05:25.357
We want to explore
and have experiences

05:25.359 --> 05:26.758
and learn new things.

05:26.760 --> 05:29.761
Kingdoms made of candy,
beautiful dragons,

05:29.763 --> 05:33.365
fire-breathing princesses,
incredibly sad wizards --

05:33.367 --> 05:35.667
<i>It's all waiting for you</i>
<i>across the ocean.</i>

05:35.669 --> 05:37.469
<i>So misguided.</i>

05:37.471 --> 05:39.437
<i>Hey,</i>
<i>this guy is great!</i>

05:39.439 --> 05:42.040
<i>What are we</i>
<i>hanging around here for?</i>

05:42.042 --> 05:43.708
[ <i>Crowd murmuring</i> ]
<i>What?!</i>

05:43.710 --> 05:46.344
<i>I did want to leave the island</i>
<i>when I was younger, but --</i>

05:46.346 --> 05:48.680
<i>You can leave now.</i>
<i>Just come with me.</i>

05:48.682 --> 05:51.282
[ <i>Crowd cheering</i> ]
<i>They're actually</i>
<i>listening to him.</i>

05:51.284 --> 05:53.284
<i>All aboard!</i>

05:53.286 --> 05:54.986
[ <i>Cheering continues</i> ]

05:54.988 --> 05:57.822
[ Feedback ]
<i>Patch me in</i>
<i>to all Minerva bots.</i>

05:57.824 --> 05:59.491
<i>Attention!</i>

05:59.493 --> 06:03.061
For your protection, the entire
<i>population of the islands</i>

06:03.063 --> 06:04.696
<i>will now be uploaded.</i>

06:11.504 --> 06:14.372
<i>Once the field</i>
<i>has reached peak saturation,</i>

06:14.374 --> 06:17.876
Doop! Rrrr! Vroom!
the brain maps of every citizen
will be simultaneously captured

06:17.878 --> 06:21.146
<i>and preserved in</i>
<i>the island chain brain frame.</i>

06:21.148 --> 06:23.415
<i>Say goodbye</i>
<i>to your meat bodies!</i>

06:23.417 --> 06:26.017
[ Crowd whimpering ]

06:26.019 --> 06:27.018
Mom!

06:27.020 --> 06:30.288
[ Whimpering continues ]

06:33.059 --> 06:34.993
Stop!

06:34.995 --> 06:37.562
<i>Hey! There's my boy!</i>

06:37.564 --> 06:39.564
Your cloud is
freaking us all out!

06:39.566 --> 06:41.733
<i>Sweetie, you forced my hand.</i>

06:41.735 --> 06:45.470
<i>This is the only way</i>
<i>I can protect you.</i>

06:46.572 --> 06:49.574
You're only doing this
because I said I wouldn't stay.

06:49.576 --> 06:50.708
So I'll stay.

06:50.710 --> 06:53.111
Just promise
to stop messing with people.

06:53.113 --> 06:55.013
<i>I'm</i> helping <i>people.</i>

06:55.015 --> 06:57.515
I know
about helping people.

06:58.684 --> 07:00.552
[ Zap ]

07:12.431 --> 07:16.468
<i>Finn, you -- you grew up</i>
<i>to be a helper, too?</i>

07:17.703 --> 07:20.472
<i>If your world taught you</i>
<i>to behave like that,</i>

07:20.474 --> 07:23.108
<i>maybe it's not all bad.</i>

07:23.110 --> 07:26.811
[ All screaming ]

07:27.980 --> 07:30.381
Vroom! Vroom!
[ Imitates tires screeching ]

07:31.217 --> 07:32.817
<i>Perhaps I acted rashly.</i>

07:32.819 --> 07:35.386
<i>I just didn't want</i>
<i>to lose you again.</i>

07:35.388 --> 07:38.890
<i>But I'll do everything I can</i>
<i>to help you leave this island.</i>

07:40.259 --> 07:42.594
I don't have to leave...
<i>right</i> away.

07:42.596 --> 07:45.563
I mean...
you're my mom.

07:49.101 --> 07:51.236
[ Crowd murmuring ]

07:51.238 --> 07:52.937
Ahoy!

07:52.939 --> 07:55.473
Now boarding the historic voyage
of the humans

07:55.475 --> 07:57.642
back to the land of Ooo!

07:58.444 --> 08:00.311
Oh, you mean
right now?

08:00.313 --> 08:02.413
I thought you meant, like,
in a while.

08:02.415 --> 08:04.849
I've still got some things
to finish up.

08:04.851 --> 08:07.118
We should definitely
keep in touch, though.

08:07.120 --> 08:10.488
[ Crowd murmuring ]

08:10.490 --> 08:13.791
You can't teach a fish to dance
<i>overnight, son.</i>

08:13.793 --> 08:16.661
Well, as long as
they got the option.

08:16.663 --> 08:17.762
Ready, Frieda?

08:17.764 --> 08:19.297
Ready.

08:19.299 --> 08:20.965
[ Boat horn blows ]

08:20.967 --> 08:23.001
Finn:
I'm leaving the island.

08:23.003 --> 08:25.470
I'm leaving my mom.

08:25.472 --> 08:28.306
What a wild adventure,
yellow stretching dog.

08:28.308 --> 08:30.375
You said it,
beautiful baby boy.

08:30.377 --> 08:32.443
[ Rumbling ]
Huh?    Huh?

08:36.682 --> 08:37.782
Oh, yeah.

08:44.156 --> 08:45.723
Frieda: Psych!

08:47.059 --> 08:48.860
Ha ha! That's right!

08:48.862 --> 08:51.062
You got fooled by Frieda!

09:01.373 --> 09:03.041
Hey, buddy.

09:04.009 --> 09:04.976
Aaah!

09:07.012 --> 09:08.346
Yaaaaaah...

09:08.348 --> 09:09.347
Aaaaaah...

09:09.349 --> 09:10.682
...aaaaaah!

09:10.684 --> 09:12.150
...aaaaaah!

09:12.152 --> 09:13.418
Huh?

09:14.520 --> 09:16.321
Patching her in now.

09:17.823 --> 09:20.758
<i>Guardian, you have done</i>
<i>just a terrific job,</i>

09:20.760 --> 09:22.927
<i>but it's time to stand down.</i>

09:30.102 --> 09:32.237
[ Boat horn blows ]

09:32.239 --> 09:35.340
When do I fire
the torpedoes?

09:36.108 --> 09:37.709
Kara, you ready to go?

09:37.711 --> 09:41.613
Actually, I think we're headed
in a different direction.

09:41.615 --> 09:44.616
Time for <i>new</i> memories.

09:48.254 --> 09:51.356
So, where are we going,
Kara?

09:51.358 --> 09:52.724
I've been thinking --

09:52.726 --> 09:55.393
I kind of like "Susan"
better.

09:55.395 --> 09:56.995
Okay, Susan.

10:05.804 --> 10:07.405
Hmm. Homey.

10:07.407 --> 10:08.873
It   <i>wa.</i>

10:10.876 --> 10:12.644
Take care of yourself
in Ooo.

10:12.646 --> 10:14.646
Be careful
when you're eating blueberries.

10:14.648 --> 10:16.981
Too many
can hurt your tummy.

10:18.917 --> 10:21.252
Your ship is moving
out of range.

10:21.254 --> 10:23.087
Is this...really you?

10:23.089 --> 10:25.423
Once you uploaded your brain
and stuff, like,

10:25.425 --> 10:27.292
are you still
the same person?

10:27.294 --> 10:30.495
I don't know for sure,
but I <i>feel</i> like it's me.

10:30.497 --> 10:32.697
I hope that's enough.

10:35.334 --> 10:37.468
Goodbye.

10:54.486 --> 10:56.821
This party is so crazy!
